Tox:
https://tox.chat/

It does not support symmetric encryption (everything is encrypted with =
public=20
key crypto), but if you have a pre-shared secret, you can use some othe=
r=20
channel (say, e-mail with contents encrypted symmetrically) to share To=
xIDs.=20
Then, add people to a Groupchat and you're good to go.

